Johnthe ripper

	a tool used for bruteforcing passwords and hashes
	
usage 
	Usage: john [OPTIONS] [PASSWORD-FILES]
	






ssh key decryption 

/usr/share/john/ssh2john.py
sudo /usr/share/john/ssh2john.py id_rsa > forjohn.txt
	id_rsa contains the ssh key 
sudo /opt/johntheripper/run/john forjohn.txt --wordlist=/download/rockyou.txt



